3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning representations of objects. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating photo-realistic images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image datasets and generating images.
